                            <comment id="115500" author="jamesanunez" created="Fri, 15 May 2015 16:40:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In the suite_stdout log for &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/ee1af5b4-fa98-11e4-828f-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/ee1af5b4-fa98-11e4-828f-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;, we see an error for getfacl:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;23:56:11:CMD: shadow-14vm6.shadow.whamcloud.com getfacl /mnt/lustre/d23.sanity-sec/f23.sanity-sec
