&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;which corresponds with the client being evicted:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;23:56:05:LustreError: 11-0: lustre-OST0000-osc-ffff88006bfbec00: operation ldlm_enqueue to node 10.1.4.165@tcp failed: rc = -107
23:56:05:Lustre: lustre-OST0000-osc-ffff88006bfbec00: Connection to lustre-OST0000 (at 10.1.4.165@tcp) was lost; in progress operations using this service will wait for recovery to complete
23:57:17:LustreError: 167-0: lustre-OST0000-osc-ffff88006bfbec00: This client was evicted by lustre-OST0000; in progress operations using this service will fail.
23:57:17:Lustre: lustre-OST0000-osc-ffff88006bfbec00: Connection restored to lustre-OST0000 (at 10.1.4.165@tcp)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
